{"tid":1211333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成班香港人又要扮野轉fb頭像 又要淆哂底","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T17:30:09.000Z","uid":18444,"like":125,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6d1fd20706c10326f59e9b0fdc68423f0e14578e","tid":1211333,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"個個琴晚今朝懶係關心香港用特效轉頭像<br />\n轉個頭比人瘋傳話犯法 即刻轉返哂普通相<br />\n<br />\n一張普通既黑色花花相 <br />\n我唔明白有咩會令到你犯法<br />\n人話犯法 d人無經過思考<br />\n淨係識跟風轉相又要驚又要唔諗<br />\n同今日淨係響金鐘食花生打卡既人有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n吖，唔係，係仲衰過出黎果d人<br />\n人地起碼都叫付出過汗水同時間<br />\n你地只係郁下隻手指 連跟風都on99咁<br />\n<br />\n由此可見，香港未來靠呢班偽善、淨係得把口<br />\n連一張相都驚比政府入罪既人<br />\n又如何去推翻送中呢條惡例？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82bf3933cd7e9b81c2d9a3c5caee62ed1397dda1","tid":1211333,"uid":118806,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:31:44.000Z","msg":"agger...<br />\n又要抗爭又唔肯付出<br />\n不過唔好嘥氣去屌佢哋喇"},{"pid":"b55e0cf4d24f477f950e781b0987dc1332e3c898","tid":1211333,"uid":114097,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:31:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n又怕痕又怕痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：用緊"},{"pid":"57d7485e5a988887b8fbc6f448bf6cc3598a8de5","tid":1211333,"uid":229425,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"發夢帶左好多頭盔出黎，放鐵馬。<br />\n冇轉icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687da29c86b2cfdcde0edd9231116282a1083bf8","tid":1211333,"uid":36236,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:32:29.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要串人唔轉唔關心件事<br />\n<br />\n人哋出咗去同你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ecc2e88bdbc63996739618bd4da8409dd7422c1","tid":1211333,"uid":226955,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15